2004-12-05 22:12:44  Rev 6441   josef

	* ggzboard/net_reversi.py:
	  - pseudo network handling for Reversi
	  This is the code as used in Escape-SDL, Xadrez-Chines etc...
	  but in a more object oriented manner, moving the common network 
	  handling to
	  two base classes (NetworkBase, NetworkInfo) and only leaving the 
	  game-specific
	  details to each game.
	  These details must then be abstracted for GGZBoard to the lowest 
	  common
	  denominator: player names, state, sending and receiving moves...


